    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>When I woke up, I noticed a strange hole in the ceiling of my room...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331450/extras/acebad0174221906852b426bb398823c.avif?t=1760186344\" width=648 height=320 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My name is James. I don’t know why I’m here, nor do I know what’s behind this door! I’m trapped in a colorless space with strange lines an environment that resembles my room, except with a hole in the ceiling. A strange object covers the hole to keep the light from coming in. The only thing I know is that I’m not alone here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331450/extras/5dbb6c52e58d67eaec99e92aec30f27f.poster.avif?t=1760186344\" width=606 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331450/extras/5dbb6c52e58d67eaec99e92aec30f27f.webm?t=1760186344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331450/extras/5dbb6c52e58d67eaec99e92aec30f27f.mp4?t=1760186344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to experience a dark, intricate atmosphere? Explore strange, dark spaces, solve puzzles, and use different items to unlock doors. But remember, you’re not alone! So, hide whenever you sense danger. Find a way out as quickly as possible, before the strange, dark creature finds you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331450/extras/057e4365166a84151a8833deb569de49.poster.avif?t=1760186344\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331450/extras/057e4365166a84151a8833deb569de49.webm?t=1760186344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331450/extras/057e4365166a84151a8833deb569de49.mp4?t=1760186344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;<strong>A Hole in My Room</strong>&quot; is a Psychological Horror game currently in development across multiple chapters. In each chapter, players must solve unique puzzles, hide from lurking enemies, find hidden objects, and uncover the secret behind the game’s story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331450/extras/7fd7778463d441c514e84b34cca6b300.poster.avif?t=1760186344\" width=612 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331450/extras/7fd7778463d441c514e84b34cca6b300.webm?t=1760186344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331450/extras/7fd7778463d441c514e84b34cca6b300.mp4?t=1760186344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re not alone, but who or what is looking  for you?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331450/extras/79c8e0348ee35796fa3077380cb0f5b6.poster.avif?t=1760186344\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331450/extras/79c8e0348ee35796fa3077380cb0f5b6.webm?t=1760186344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331450/extras/79c8e0348ee35796fa3077380cb0f5b6.mp4?t=1760186344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First Chapter Features :</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Duration: ~ 30min</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Discover story of the first chapter</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Solve some different puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Find hidden objects</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Open locked doors</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Hide from enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Enjoy the stylized graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
